::KitKat::
She looked at Destructor, her face pail and breathing hard. Her 
thoughts were running away with her. "No, listen to me. I don't need 
rest.  I need to find out how to destroy the clones. Before it's to 
late." She looked at Drillbit. "Listen to me. What if Megatron could 
clone more of there like himself." She looked at Destructor.  "think 
about it. An army of Megatrons. I can't sleep and let this 
possability exist. No, I must finish this work."

She was scared about this possability, and she didn't care if it 
showed.  She didn't want an all out clone war to break out.
